quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,Diggah Yalli maqaanek ken kah amrisem abaah usuk ken kak waaseemik yaxxeere mari jannootaa kee gexxa daroorih addal yan
  15,46,"Kulli umaanek nagaynan luk, kulli digaalák amaanah anuk tet (jannoota kinnuk) cula keenik iyyan"
  15,47,ken (moominiin kinnuk) lubbittek baguumaanee kee kuuxewaynan kalleh usun toobokoh anuk kacanu luk qaraakiy amol itta fan wagitak daffeyan jannat addal
  15,48,Usun tet (Jannoota kinnuk) addal taqabii kee Saqsaqitik tu ken elle maxagtaay usun teetik inkinnah yawqe mara hinnon
  15,49,"Nabiyow Yi naqoosah waris, diggah anu dambi cabti li xuwaw li kinniyom yol gace marah"
  15,50,Nabiyow diggah Yi digaala is qansarissa digaala kinnim keenih waris yol gacam cine marah
  15,51,"Nabii Mucammadow ġcsaseio Nabii Ibraahim qibinih (malayka Kinnuk) xaagu keenih waris, Yalli Nabii Ibraahim baxa geyuwaamih ayti kumaa kee Nabii Luut marih baysah ken ruube waqdi"
  15,52,"Malayka kaal culteeh salaamaqle kaal qidde waqdi salaąaamaqle keenih yukkuqeeh maaqo keenih xayyoyse, tokkel woo maaqo isik akmewaanam keenik yuble waqdi, diggah nanu siinik meesitnah keenik iyye"
  15,53,"Malayka Nabii Ibraahimik :ma meesitin diggah nanu kol kah nemeetem ixxiga le baxal koo ayti kumusnamkeh iyyaanama kaak itte"
  15,54,"Nabii Ibraahim qajjibsitak : idoolanni yoo kee yi barra inkih geek lakalaa isin baxal yoo aytikumussaanam ?Ah anninnah tan aytikumaay yoh abtaanam keenik iyye"
  15,55,"Malayka Ibraahimow nummah asmatleemiy raq sinnil koo ayti kumusnak, toysa atu nanu koo elle aytikumusnaamak yabboode marih num makkin kaak itte"
  15,56,Nabii Ibraahim isi Rabbih Racmatak iyyi yabboodee makkoote maray tirtô gitak makkoote akke waytek keenik iyye
  15,57,Yallih xaquk rubsumte malaykay isin yoo elle aytikumusseenimik kalah edde temeeten caagid siinik macaay keenik iyye
  15,58,Diggah Nanu umeyniitih yan marâ fanah rubsumne ken fingisnankeh kaak itte malayka
  15,59,Nabii Luutu kee kay buxah marak kaal teemenem kee keenik kalah kay marak kaal teemeneemiy nanu finqak inkih naggosnu wayna akke waytek
  15,60,Kinnih immay kay barray koroositte diggah is raqqa iyye marâ lih raqtam teetil mekelle digaalat